#BITAPP
Application is built on the cordova platform, which provides the application to be built for different platforms.
The application has some files in the BITWEB directory, which provide App with the data from the server and helps manipulate database,
the files that begin with the "app-*.php" are the files that are necessary for this application. 

The application has been tested on the most of the current working platforms, and it works perfectly fine with little or no change.
The application has been tested on devices like iPhone 6s, 6 Plus, 6, 5s, 5 and on Android Nexus 6P, 5x, 5, Galaxy Note II, S5.

All the files in this BITAPP folder are to be copied to the www folder of your cordova project.
